The Hero Band system represents a comprehensive approach to industrial IoT,
combining wearable technology, real-time data processing, and intuitive 
dashboard interfaces to enhance workplace safety and operational efficiency.

For more information about the Big Hero team and the Hero Band project:
- GitHub: https://github.com/big-hero-senai
